             were indicted for <rs id="t17861213-81-off419" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17861213-81-off419" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17861213-81-off419" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
