                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861213-81-off419 t17861213-81-cd420"></join>, twenty-eight pounds weight of rope called cable rope, value 4 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the property of the 
               <persName id="t17861213-81-victim712" type="victimName">
                     <rs id="t17861213-81-viclabel421" type="occupation">Master and Brothers of the Trinity house</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861213-81-victim712 t17861213-81-viclabel421"></join>
